What is Dasom?
--------------

Dasom is an input method framework.
Now we can test Dasom.


INSTALL
-------

  * Compile

    ./autogen.sh
    make
    sudo make install
    sudo ldconfig

  * For using symbols in Jeongeum Engine

    wget https://raw.githubusercontent.com/choehwanjin/libhangul/master/data/hanja/mssymbol.txt
    sudo mv mssymbol.txt /usr/share/libhangul/hanja/
    ls /usr/share/libhangul/hanja/mssymbol.txt

  * Enabling dasom-agent@gnome-shell-extensions.cogno.org

    gnome-shell-extension-tool -e dasom-agent@gnome-shell-extensions.cogno.org

  * Update your gtk module cache

    debian / ubuntu 32-bit

      sudo /usr/lib/i386-linux-gnu/libgtk-3-0/gtk-query-immodules-3.0 --update-cache
      sudo /usr/lib/i386-linux-gnu/libgtk2.0-0/gtk-query-immodules-2.0 --update-cache

    debian / ubuntu64-bit

      sudo /usr/lib/x86_64-linux-gnu/libgtk-3-0/gtk-query-immodules-3.0 --update-cache
      sudo /usr/lib/x86_64-linux-gnu/libgtk2.0-0/gtk-query-immodules-2.0 --update-cache

    Arch Linux

      sudo /usr/bin/gtk-query-immodules-3.0 --update-cache
      sudo /usr/bin/gtk-query-immodules-2.0 --update-cache

  * Configuration im-config

    im-config

  * Then, select Dasom, logout and login.


Troubleshoot
------------

* Failed to load shared library
  Check /etc/ld.so.conf and /etc/ld.so.conf.d/ for /usr/local/lib path


Architecture
------------

     +-- im modules --+    +--- each processes ----+  +- a process --+
     | gtk2 im module |    | gnome-shell-extension |  |   X server   |
     | gtk3 im module |    | dasom-indicator       |  +--------------+
     | qt4  im module |    +-----------------------+         ^ |
     +----------------+                |                     | |
              |                        |                     | |
              | calls                  | calls               | |
              |                        |                     | |
    +------------------+    +---------------------+          | |
    | dasom IM library |    | dasom agent library |          | | communicates
    +------------------+    +---------------------+          | |
             ^ |                      ^ |                    | |
             | |   communicates       | |                    | |
             | |   via Unix Socket    | |                    | |
             | v                      | v                    | v
          +---------------------- a process ----------------------+
          |                     dasom-daemon (including XIM)      |
          +-------------------------------------------------------+
                          |                        |
                          | calls                  | create instance
                          | singleton instance     | (not module yet)
                +---------------+            +------------------+
                | engine module |   calls    | candidate module |
                |   interface   | ---------> |    interface     |
                +---------------+            +------------------+
                  |                            |
                  +- dasom-english             +- dasom-candidate (gtk3)
                  +- dasom-jeongeum


Debugging
---------
    export GTK_IM_MODULE="dasom"
    export QT4_IM_MODULE="dasom"
    export G_MESSAGES_DEBUG=dasom
    export XMODIFIERS="@im=dasom"
    gedit


